## KEY RULES

1. **File boundaries** — content/markup lives in `index.html`, styles in `css/`, scripts in `js/main.js`, Cloudflare config in `_headers`/`_redirects`/`wrangler.toml`. Do not re-inline styles or scripts.
2. **Mobile/desktop parity** — any UI change to a desktop layout section must include the matching mobile responsive change in the same diff. Validator will catch violations.
3. **Email protection intact** — Cloudflare `email-decode.min.js` script tag and encoded email in `index.html` must survive every diff.
4. **No technical claim edits without owner sign-off** — case study metrics (e.g. "71% TTFB reduction") are verifiable claims; flag to owner before changing.
5. **CSP hygiene** — when adding new external origins to `index.html` or `css/`, update `_headers` CSP in the same diff.

---

## SHARED FILES — ROUTING NOTES

All god nodes live in the `index.html` / `css/` / `js/` / `_headers` cluster. Any task touching these files is potential god-node contact — declare in ROUTE block before writing.

Security-related changes (CSP in `_headers`, new external script/style origins, auth references): route to `@security-engineer` in parallel.

---

## WORKFLOW

For every task:
1. Identify which sections of `salvatorepesti.com.html` are affected
2. Check god node contact — if any god node is in scope, declare in task description
3. Check mobile/desktop parity — any layout change needs both views
4. Produce complete diff covering ALL affected sections
5. Run validator: `git diff | python3 tools/validator.py`
6. On PASS: apply + `graphify update .`

---

## COMMON TASKS

| Task | File | Key section / element |
|------|------|-----------------------|
| Update case study content | `index.html` | `.case` sections in body |
| Edit bio / hero copy | `index.html` | `.hero` or `#about` section |
| Add/modify navigation links | `index.html` | `.rail-inner` nav element |
| Tune performance (preconnect, font loading) | `index.html` + `css/fonts.css` | `<head>` link tags |
| Update security / cache headers | `_headers` | CSP, Cache-Control directives |
| Adjust live clock (timezone, format) | `js/main.js` | `clock()` IIFE |
| Update contact / email | `index.html` | Cloudflare-encoded email anchor + `email-decode.min.js` script tag |
| Add scroll reveal to new section | `index.html` | add `.reveal` class; `js/main.js` handles it automatically |
| Add new styles | `css/main.css` | relevant section comment block |
